export const questionObj = {"Qtext": "
 
If it is given that \(w : x :: y : z \), then prove that
\[
	\frac{4w + 7x }{4y + 7z } = \frac{4w - 7x }{4y - 7z }
\]
\newline

", "Steps": [{"id": "s1", "n_params": 0, "step_txt": "
It is given that
\[
	\frac{w }{x } = \frac{y }{z }
\]
\[
	\Rightarrow \frac{4 w }{7 x } = \frac{4 y }{7 z }
\]
\[
	\Rightarrow \frac{4 w + 7 x }{4 w - 7 x } = \frac{4 y + 7 z }{4 y - 7 z } \textrm{ {by componendo and dividendo}}
\]
\[
	\Rightarrow \frac{4 w + 7 x }{4 y + 7 z } = \frac{4 w - 7 x }{4 y - 7 z }
\]
Hence proved.
\newline

"}]} 

 export const resp = [{"data": [], "text": " "}]
